{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Mac OS X and iPhone OS have a rich model for processing and presenting language and locale-specific information such as dates, times, numbers, calendars, and time zones. Avoiding common mistakes when handling international data is critical to making your application ready for a global audience. Get the detailed knowledge you need to make your application shine no matter where in the world your users are."}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-125-internationalizing-data-on-mac-and-iphone"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC10","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Internationalizing Data on Mac and iPhone"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-125-Internationalizing-Data-on-Mac-and-iPhone","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/125\/","type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"references":{"WWDC10.jpeg":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC10.jpeg","alt":null}